  Getting Started  A simple Object Oriented PHP Client for   Cloudflare API .
This package provides convenient access to the Cloudflare REST API using PHP.  Installation  Install   php-cloudflare-api  via Composer:     composer   require   sergkeim/php-cloudflare-api
  The full Installation of this package can be found   here .  Usage  The full Usage of this package can be found   here .     <?  php

   use   Cloudflare\Client  ;

   $client   =   new   Client  (  'CLOUDFLARE_TOKEN'  );

   $response   =   $client  ->  accounts  ()  ->  list  ();

   $results   =   $response  ->  json  (  'results'  );
